column5: Well, here's my 2nd fishing video.  It's from a single catch of a muskie during the 2010 season.  Hope you enjoy!  <iframe width="420" height="315" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/YJgCSVra78E" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>  . . . . . . . . . . . .... aaaaaaand, in case you missed it, my first video.
